        <div id="process" class="page">
          <div class="description">
            <p> Our design process ensures that the right things get done at the
              right time. It makes design predictable and manageable, and also
              frees our designers to do what they do best — design awesome products. </p>
          </div>
          <div class="content">
            <div class="analysis-and-insight">
              <h4>I  Analysis &amp; Insight</h4>
              <p> Through research and observations of the existing ecosystem we look: </p>
              <p> <strong>1—</strong>inside the company to understand the business case,
                context and processes where the new product or service will be deployed, and <br />
                <strong>2—</strong>outside to the ecosystem, market environment and culture. </p>
              <!--
								<p>
									<strong>Outcomes</strong>: design drivers, research data, images, models, directions,
									ideas, impressions, personas, stories, high level flows
								</p>
								-->
            </div>
            <div class="concept-design">
              <h4>II Concept Design</h4>
              <p> We use a design approach to find and invent new patterns, flows
                and frameworks for the future product or service. </p>
              <p> <strong>Outcomes</strong>: frameworks &amp; concepts, journeys, maps, principles,
                constraints, identities, task flows, requirements </p>
            </div>
            <div class="detailed-design">
              <h4>III Detailed Design</h4>
              <p> Based on the two previous phases, we design and deliver
                solutions that can be either a </p>
              <p> <strong>1—</strong>Final concept presentation, or<br />
                <strong>2—</strong>Final product or service specification and production assets </p>
              <p><strong>Outcomes</strong>: product or service specifications, experiences, interfaces, metrics</p>
            </div>
            <div class="implementation">
              <h4>IV Implementation</h4>
              <p> We participate in the implementation process and produce
                pixel-perfect graphics and refined interaction, i.e. as an
                integral part of an agile development team. We ensure that the
                design is implemented as intended: functional and beautiful. </p>
              <p><strong>Outcomes</strong>: refined specifications, product graphics, design support</p>
           </div>
          </div>
        </div>
